 planetary atmosphere and MHD stellar wind interaction models\ntogether with UV observations. In particular, we find that HD 209458b should\nlikely have an intrinsic magnetic moment of 10-20% that of Jupiter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Aug 2017 17:31:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-11"}
